N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 588.9 - Cooperative agreements

State Regulations

The agency may enter and carry out written agreements with
the Federal government and/or with other State agencies in order to facilitate
cooperation and joint action to be taken under any statute administered by the
agency. Notes
